  <string name="main_step_1_text">1. Position your Android device\'s camera to monitor an area.  If you don\'t have a phone holder, <a href="https://goseumdochi.org/the-better-to-see-you-with#photo">maybe you can build one out of plastic bricks</a>?</string>
  <string name="main_step_2_text">2. Activate your paired Sphero in the middle of the area being monitored and then start the automatic setup procedure.</string>
  <string name="main_step_3_text">3. Sit back and watch what happens when intruders enter!  Don\'t forget to <a href="https://goseumdochi.org/submit-your-own-video/">capture some video footage and submit it to our website</a> :)</string>

